The owner/operator shall maintain the following monthly records in a n Air  District -approved log 
for at least two years from the date of entry . Log entries shall be retained on -site at a central 
location and made immediately available to Air District staff upon request.  
a. Hours of operation for reliability -related activities (maintenance and testing);  
b. Hours of operation for emission testing to show compliance with emission limits;  
c. Hours of operation (emergency);  
d. For each emergency, the nature of the emergency condition;  
e. Fuel usage for the engine;  and, 
f. Location and total hours of operation at each off -site location.  
